71
00:03:56,879 --> 00:04:00,159
I asked, what kind of food is a peanut?

72
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,680
Is it A, a vegetable?

73
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,719
B, a nut?

74
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,840
C, a legume.

75
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,680
What did you say, Rob?

76
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:09,920
I said C, a legume, because that was the only one I didn't know,

77
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,840
and it can't be as simple as being a nut.

78
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,039
An inspired guess.

79
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:17,439
If you said C, legume, then congratulations.

80
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:20,480
Despite the name, a peanut is not actually a nut.

81
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:25,040
Rather conveniently though, we don't have time for me to explain exactly why it's not a nut,

82
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:27,759
but I'm sure you're smart enough to look it up yourself.

83
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:29,519
So you're not going to explain it?

84
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,879
No, sorry, we don't have the time.

85
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:34,399
Sounds to me like you're allergic to hard work, Neil.

86
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:37,839
Ah, nice link to today's vocabulary.

87
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:39,199
We do have time for that.

88
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:43,040
Today we've been looking at the topic of food allergies.

89
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:46,399
This is when a particular food causes a medical problem.

90
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:50,479
The problem could be minor or it could be very serious, even fatal,

91
00:04:50,479 --> 00:04:53,279
and these are called allergic reactions.

92
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:56,639
The topic has been investigated with robust studies.

93
00:04:56,639 --> 00:05:01,120
This is research that has been done in a very detailed, accurate and thorough way.

94
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,439
The next word was the noun prevalence.

95
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:07,599
This is used to talk about how common or how frequent something is.

96
00:05:07,599 --> 00:05:12,639
In this research, they examined the prevalence of food allergies in certain age groups.

97
00:05:12,719 --> 00:05:15,839
Closely connected to food allergies is eczema.

98
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:22,000
This is a medical condition that makes your skin dry, painful and itchy over different parts of the body.

99
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:26,319
It was reported that there had been a significant increase in the number of people

100
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:28,800
suffering from eczema and food allergies.

101
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:32,479
A significant increase is a big and important increase.

102
00:05:32,479 --> 00:05:36,399
And finally, we had the phrase to put something down to something.

103
00:05:36,399 --> 00:05:39,759
This means to say one thing is the reason for another.

104
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:44,319
